锁代码之外没有使用设备。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-01/49daf380-9d94-11ed-9bbf-5da856c4f895" alt="六个获胜的移动电源排列在一张木桌上，背景是室内植物" data-uuid="6d695920-f41f-318a-959b-2c69a55bb3d2"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">艾米·斯科海姆 / Engadget</div></figure><p>我使用每个移动电源附带的电缆为 Galaxy S22 Ultra、MacBook Pro 和 iPad Air 充电。对于 iPhone，我使用 Apple 提供的 USB-C 转 Lighting 线缆。对于不包含电源线或包含 USB-C 至 USB-A 连接器的低容量移动电源，我使用了这款<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:nimble;elmt:;cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=88872e72-f0df-4301-b936-bf22f074034c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=nimble&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5nb25pbWJsZS5jb20vY29sbGVjdGlvbnMvdXNiLWMtY2FibGVzL3Byb2R1Y3RzL3VzYi1jLWNhYmxlLXBvd2Vya25pdCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMTE0OWQxOGEtMzY2ZC00MWU3LTljZmEtN2NlNGQwZmQ2ODM1In0&amp;signature=AQAAAWJmFK5yLOrU_OxXHu5r_FfdjuwPrTE0Drz9ZoHY5j4C&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gonimble.com%2Fcollections%2Fusb-c-cables%2Fproducts%2Fusb-c-cable-powerknit" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.gonimble.com/collections/usb-c-cables/products/usb-c-cable-powerknit">额定 60W 的 USB-C 至 USB-C 线缆</a>。</p><p>作为参考，以下是我们用于测试的每台设备的电池容量：</p><ul><li><p> iPhone 11：3,110 毫安时</p></li><li><p>iPhone 14 Plus：4,325 毫安时</p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:;cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5zYW1zdW5nLmNvbS9sZXZhbnQvc21hcnRwaG9uZXMvZ2FsYXh5LXMyMi11bHRyYS9zcGVjcy8iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjExNDlkMThhLTM2NmQtNDFlNy05Y2ZhLTdjZTRkMGZkNjgzNSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAUE_86A1qR0wY6DVI6LfXaDw8TRY5E558BqSIlK48JRV&amp;gcReferre